n welfare indicators for market weight pigs. <em>Transl. Anim. Sci.</em> 1, 533-558.</li><li>Elanco<sup>TM</sup>, Paylean<sup>TM</sup> 45: Ractopamine hydrochloride Type A medicated article.</li><li>Wu M., Deng J., Chen Y., Chu W., Hung D. and Yang C. 2013, Late diagnosis of an outbreak of leanness-enhancing agent-related food poisoning. <em>Am. J. Emerg. Med.</em> 10:1501-1503.</li></ol>
